{"tid":1918421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪中左武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-10T05:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T18:01:27.000Z","uid":270161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fc38a772da5c916d46975ac299208f15f9405e","tid":1918421,"uid":270161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:52:03.000Z","msg":"好撚驚中左<br />\n我呢兩日心口覺得有啲悶 <br />\n吸氣個陣有少少痛 <br />\n喉嚨又有少少腫 <br />\n不過就冇發燒冇肚屙冇咳<br />\n(早兩日我係屋企自己飲左兩三杯燒酒bomb之後就咁)<br />\n屌 好撚驚 <br />\n我已經極少出街 毒撚留係屋企 <br />\n戴好口罩做足曬所有防護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人話我知我應該點做<br />\n好慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c51a73e80c63225e552bc50b1cf42494decc25","tid":1918421,"uid":143284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"感冒都會咁架啦，邊有咁易中，我前幾個禮拜咳足一個月仲驚過你，睇兩次醫生，而家都好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好自己嚇自己"},{"pid":"30eb4495c03230ac07f084f4a1fd69b6e29ecdfc","tid":1918421,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"去政府診所有得留口水驗<br />\n走去驗下好過日日驚"},{"pid":"f803585525d9d36f9b9c3003e99c0a47ffb6be38","tid":1918421,"uid":145868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:00:53.000Z","msg":"去狗屋報定案先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c84706b4b415955264f881373ffafcad2c6899e","tid":1918421,"uid":22590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:05:54.000Z","msg":"去就近差館(狗屋)查詢, 警員(狗)有全港最優良防疫設備同對武漢肺炎既認識, 一定要去問專業意見"},{"pid":"c74a157758657143bc0d0b485ba60ea28c1aa823","tid":1918421,"uid":270161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07c51a73e80c63225e552bc50b1cf42494decc25","tid":1918421,"uid":143284,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"感冒都會咁架啦，邊有咁易中，我前幾個禮拜咳足一個月仲驚過你，睇兩次醫生，而家都好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /